name: arnav12's team library
description:
The canon mg2520 driver is also called the Canon PIXMA MG2520 printer. It is a compact entry-level multifunction printer. Works on Windows 10, Windows 8.1, Windows 8, Windows 7, Windows Vista and Windows XP.

If your Canon printer does not work properly, for example you see some errors in the print test, the printer status is offline, you need to consider updating the printer driver.
